<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Contact Us | The Learning Sphere</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --text: #111111;
      --muted: #666666;
      --accent: #000000;
      --border: #e0e0e0;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      font-size: 16px;
    }

    .wrapper {
      max-width: 750px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 40px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    p {
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .contact-details {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .detail {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    .label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--text);
    }

    .value {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    footer {
      margin-top: 60px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <h1>Contact Us</h1>
    <p>If you have any questions, feedback, or collaboration inquiries â€” feel free to reach out. We're here to help.</p>

    <div class="contact-details">
      <div class="detail">
        <span class="label">Email:</span>
        <span class="value">support@learningsphere.in</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail">
        <span class="label">Phone:</span>
        <span class="value">will be available soon</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail">
        <span class="label">Office Hours:</span>
        <span class="value">24/7 Available for you</span>
      </div>
      <div class="detail">
        <span class="label">Address:</span>
        <span class="value">Available only in Online mode</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
      &copy; {{year}} The Learning Sphere. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
